snippet.title: SOKOCAT - ISLANDS [STEAM TRAILER]
snippet.description:
A relaxing minimalist Sokoban-style puzzle. You have to push the stone blocks to their right positions on the island, you can use bridges to reach the next island or elevators to go up and down hills.

Game page:
https://www.risingmoongames.com/our-games/sokocat-islands
